      <para id="id7969732">(d) <emphasis effect="bold">Your last assignment in this module: </emphasis>Supposing that the community wants to expand / improve these services after a year or two, or add further services, suggest ways in which you could obtain the money that will be needed?</para>
      <para id="id4649351">Study the sketch on page 6 once again and put forward some ideas for fundraising projects. Remember the specific location of the community and study the environment surrounding Cathcart – there may be opportunities that could be used to draw people and money.</para>
